songs.title: Rooh (Soul)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Tu...
Khendi Sun Laye Bathere
Vey Mein Jhoote Laare Tere Raje Yaar
Tu...
Nalle Morh Challi ,Tohfe Jehre
Tenu Mene Ditte Herriye
Tu...
Chad Ja, Chad Na
Soukha Tere Vaste, Soniye
Tu...
Billo Yaad Rakhi, Appa Kehre
Tere Piche Mar Challe

[Hook]
Aje V Teri Yaad Aaye, Dildar
Kinne Tere Baad Aaye Tu
Jaddo Di Methu Rus Ke Gayi Rooh
Tu Dil Vichu Kad Lai Gayi
Na Mille Mainu Apna Pata
Na Jag De Aitbara Ne Tu
Jaddo Di Methu Rus Ke Gayi Rooh
Tu Dil Vichu Kad Lai Gayi
